</P>
<P>
-- In a dramatic reversal, the Senate yesterday overwhelmingly
approved the Clinton administration's full request for 34 million
dollars to crack down on cigarettes sales to teenagers.
</P>
<P>
-- More than 60 died as three survived the crash of a
Vietnamese jetliner in Phnom Penh, the Cambodia capital.
</P>
