<HEADLINE> 3 Israeli Citizens Seek Political Asylum </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
JERUSALEM, September 4 (Xinhua) -- Three Israeli citizens
sought political asylum today at the territories of the
Palestinian National Authority (PNA), reported the Jerusalem
Media and Communication Center here.
</P>
<P>
The three Israelis are now in the Military College of
Palestinian Preventive Security Apparatus in Jericho, West
Bank, while Palestinian and Israeli contacts are being held to
solve the matter, the center said.
</P>
<P>
The names of the three Israelis are not disclosed for
security reasons and no additional details are available so
far. 
