<HEADLINE> NZ Stocks Finish Lower </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WELLINGTON, September 4 (Xinhua) -- The New Zealand sharemarket
ended lower today with investors digesting the as-expected profit
result of Brierley Investment, which went up just 1 million NZ
dollars (630,000 US dollars) from last year.
</P>
