<HEADLINE> Riot Forces Abandonment of Conmebol Game </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BUENOS AIRES, September 4 (Xinhua) -- A riot by agnry fans
forced the abandonment of a Conmebol Cup match between Paraguay's
Sportivo Luqueno and Brazil's Vitoria in Asuncion, Paraguay, on
Wednesday, according to reports reaching here.
</P>
