<HEADLINE> Results of the US Open Tennis (1) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, September 3 (Xinhua) -- Following are the results
at the U.S. Open tennis championships on Wednesday (prefix number
denotes seeding):
</P>
<P>
Women's singles, quarter-finals
</P>
<P>
